c: 24
v: 63
t: "Mulakhola omulango kwomurumwa shinga omulango kwenyu abeene khu beene tawe. Toto Nyasaye amanyile balia barulanga mukhwiyiba mwinywe nibefisafisa. Kho (babe bukheke) berecheshele\tbalia bakhayanga amalomesio kaye, amasila kaletsa okhubanyoola nohomba shiboolele eshinyasio shiwumisinjia"